{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"625","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"全球大型科技業者給力 去年直接採購的清潔能源創新高","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2020-02-01 10:40&nbsp; </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>聯合報 編譯季晶晶／即時報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 476px;' />&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>得力於全球大型科技公司，去年直接銷售給跨國企業的清潔能源數量激增，創下新高紀錄。歐新社</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>衛報報導，在全球大型科技公司採購推動下，去年直接銷售給跨國企業的清潔能源數量激增，創下新高紀錄。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>過去兩年，由於企業對永續能源的需求增長，他們向再生能源開發商購買的清潔能源，數量已大增兩倍。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>包括谷歌、臉書、亞馬遜和微軟在內的科技巨擘為供電給他們的數據中心，成為再生能源的最大買主。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>彭博新能源（<span lang='EN-US'>BloombergNEF</span>）發現，跨國企業在過去<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>年間購買的清潔能源，超過越南或波蘭等國家的全部能源用量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據彭博新能源近日的報告，去年賣給跨國企業的再生能源裡，技科業者占四分之一左右。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>最大買主是谷歌。這家搜尋引擎巨擘使用的綠能將增加<span lang='EN-US'>40%</span>，取得額外<span lang='EN-US'>1.6GW</span>（百萬瓩）的綠色電力，相等於<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>萬個屋頂太陽能發電量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>彭博新能源發現，去年，<span lang='EN-US'>23</span>個國家的<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>家公司買進<span lang='EN-US'>19.5GW</span>的再生能源，比前年的紀錄再增加<span lang='EN-US'>40%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>這些所謂的電力收購協議（<span lang='EN-US'>PPA</span>）的交易金額可能介於<span lang='EN-US'>200</span>億<span lang='EN-US'>-300</span>億美元之間，約占<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年全球綠能投資總額的<span lang='EN-US'>10%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>電力收購協議的市場在北美呈現快速增長之勢，那裡是這類交易的主力，但在歐洲和拉丁美洲也逐漸增加。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>光是去年，就有近<span lang='EN-US'>400</span>家公司承諾要設定有實證的氣候目標，設定此目標的公司數量增加超過一倍。<span lang='EN-US'>63</span>家公司矢言購買足以<span lang='EN-US'>100%</span>滿足其能源需求的清潔能源。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>這些重視永續發展的承諾可望在未來十年，促成近<span lang='EN-US'>1000</span>億美元的清潔能源投資，在全球興建<span lang='EN-US'>105GW</span>的太陽能或風力發電廠。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4315212</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-02-03","clk_count":"146"}},"__N_SSG":true}